Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Anniversary mania
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0440fjq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Aug 1987
In the dog days of summer, even the Seven Dwarfs get to celebrate an anniversary. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.